          <stentry class="- topic/stentry " xtrf="C:\Users\sharmabi\git\documentation\helion\supportedconfigs.dita" xtrc="stentry:12;71:20">EXTERNAL_API, EXTERNAL_VM, GUEST (vxlan), MGMT on separate VLANs</stentry>
